Chance Thanks to a Mistake
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par Black played the throw-in move at \'a1\'e3 to save his stones and capture White.
\par However this move was a bi mistake.
\par
\par White got a chance because of Black's mistake.
\par How should Black play to win the capturing race?
\par
\par Pae is a failure.
\par }
