Dia. 02 Correct Answer?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Some people might think it is good if White takes at 1.
\par If Black plays dansu at 2, White wins the capturing race with 3 and 5.
\par
\par So is this the correct answer?
\par Actually not, this variation is just \cf1\b White's wishful thinking\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
