Dia. 04 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \cf1\b Making one eye\cf0\b0  with 1 is the \cf1\b maek\cf0\b0  for winning the capturing race.
\par
\par After Black 2, White fills the liberty at 3.
\par Black has two while White has three liberties, so White wins the capturing race.
\par
\par
\par }
